message: "Please cite WEAVE using the metadata below."
type: software
title: "WEAVE: Cross-Server Workflow Conformance for MCP-Based Agent Systems"
abstract: "A process-mining framework for detecting cross-server attack patterns in agent systems built on the Model Context Protocol (MCP). Includes a domain-specific language (WeaveSpec) for declaring intended agent workflows, four behavioral detection layers (conformance, statistical, sequence, causal), and longitudinal trust scoring (WeaveTrust)."
